  "description": "Bottom banner / footer chrome for the Nordstrom Price Drop Shopping Bag email. Free-shipping bar, Nordy Club loyalty line, app-store badges, social icons, legal/compliance links (privacy, view-online mirror page, and one-click unsubscribe keyed on the profile enterpriseId), mailing address, and a dynamically rendered copyright year. Brand chrome images are AEM-hosted from folder nd_shopbag_pd.",
  "fragment": {
    "content": "<div class=\"acr-fragment is-locked has-html-params\" data-fragment-id=\"ajo:SELF\"><style acrite-mso-css=\"true\"></style><div class=\"acr-fragment acr-tmp-component\" data-tmp-component-id=\"html\" data-contenteditable=\"false\"><!-- BEGIN BOTTOMBANNER -->\n{{!-- Footer chrome. Unsubscribe uses AJO one-click unsubscription (identity resolved from profile enterpriseId at send). Copyright year is rendered dynamically. --}}\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">\n  <!-- free shipping bar -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:16px 0 0;\"><a data-nl-type=\"DEEPLINK\" data-tracking-type=\"DEEPLINK\" href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/customer-service/shipping?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_freeship\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_FreeShipping_Desktop_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:7aa12690-5a98-4346-b124-3bea6c746bde\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Free shipping. Free returns. All the time.\" width=\"750\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;max-width:750px;height:auto;border:0;margin:0 auto;\"></a></td></tr>\n  <!-- Nordy Club -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:22px 24px 6px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:19px;color:#333333;\">Earn points wherever you shop with a Nordy Club membership. <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/nordyclub?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_nordyclub\" style=\"color:#111111;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;\">Learn more</a></td></tr>\n  <!-- app badges -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:14px 20px 4px;\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/nordstrom/id474349412?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_app_ios\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_App_1_Mobile_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:11526a3a-f6fd-4994-a086-c26e6775c7e6\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Download on the App Store\" height=\"40\" style=\"display:inline-block;height:40px;width:auto;border:0;vertical-align:middle;margin:0 4px;\"></a> <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nordstrom.app&{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_app_android\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_App_2_Mobile_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:76fa7a88-870b-40bf-a4a9-cf53f5380b0e\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Get it on Google Play\" height=\"40\" style=\"display:inline-block;height:40px;width:auto;border:0;vertical-align:middle;margin:0 4px;\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/nordstrom-apps?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_app_more\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_App_3_Mobile_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:36078189-6439-4142-8c1d-ba425c6634ec\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Get the Nordstrom app\" height=\"40\" style=\"display:inline-block;height:40px;width:auto;border:0;vertical-align:middle;margin:0 4px;\"></a></td></tr>\n  <!-- social icons -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:10px 20px 6px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nordstrom?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_social_fb\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_SocialIcons_1_Mobile_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:df763062-aba1-4694-ac6a-b84ab074cf3a\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Facebook\" width=\"28\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:28px;height:auto;border:0;vertical-align:middle;margin:0 6px;\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nordstrom?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_social_ig\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_SocialIcons_2_Mobile_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:862b1871-6676-4d3d-a427-86c9c7005a62\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Instagram\" width=\"28\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:28px;height:auto;border:0;vertical-align:middle;margin:0 6px;\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/nordstrom?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_social_pin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_SocialIcons_3_Mobile_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:1802bdce-61e0-47ce-9f57-4a3189f182ad\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Pinterest\" width=\"28\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:28px;height:auto;border:0;vertical-align:middle;margin:0 6px;\"></a> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/nordstrom?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_social_yt\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_SocialIcons_4_Mobile_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:37b4fac4-e9f9-4024-85a0-150b520c5d26\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"YouTube\" width=\"28\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:28px;height:auto;border:0;vertical-align:middle;margin:0 6px;\"></a></td></tr>\n  <!-- legal links -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:18px 20px 6px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:18px;color:#767676;\"><a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/privacy?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_privacy\" style=\"color:#767676;text-decoration:underline;\">Privacy Policy</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a data-nl-type=\"mirrorPage\" href=\"#view-online\" style=\"color:#767676;text-decoration:underline;\">View in browser</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a data-nl-type=\"unsubscription\" href=\"#unsubscribe\" style=\"color:#767676;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a></td></tr>\n  <!-- address + copyright -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0 20px 26px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:11px;line-height:17px;color:#999999;\">Nordstrom, Inc., 1600 Seventh Avenue, Seattle, WA 98101<br>&copy; {%= formatDate(getCurrentZonedDateTime(), \"yyyy\") %} Nordstrom, Inc. All rights reserved.</td></tr>\n</table>\n<!-- END BOTTOMBANNER --></div></div>",
